Last Usage Date = 
CALCULATE(
    MAX(Metrics[Date]),
    FILTER(
        Metrics,
        Metrics[Metric Type] = "Used Licenses"
            && Metrics[Product] = EARLIER(Metrics[Product])
    )
)

    💡 If EARLIER() causes issues (especially in measures, not columns), use this instead:

Last Usage Date = 
CALCULATE(
    MAX(Metrics[Date]),
    FILTER(
        Metrics,
        Metrics[Metric Type] = "Used Licenses"
            && Metrics[Product] = MAX(Metrics[Product])
    )
)
